"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breakdancing will be added to the rota, although baseball and Karate have been dropped from the last games.\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karate\", \"score\": 0.999999978953156, \"rank\": 2.1046853279743744e-08, \"text\": \"Karate\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rota\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"baseball\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the last games\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ButBMX,climbing, surfing and skateboarding have all retained their spots in the schedule.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their spots\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the schedule\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 32 sports, with some separated into further categories to a total of 48.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"32 sports\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"further categories\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All together there will be 329 events.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"329 events\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know about how to get tickets forParis 2024.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tickets are on sale from the official website (tickets.paris2024.org).\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tickets\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the official website\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets.paris2024.org\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 250,000 new tickets were released at 9am BST to celebrate 100 days to go, with half of those tickets on offer for \\u20ac100 or less and almost 20,000 tickets priced at \\u20ac24.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.999997746661203, \"rank\": 2.2533439477629822e-06, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 250,000 new tickets\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"100 days\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"those tickets\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"offer\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"almost 20,000 tickets\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are sold on a first-come, first-serve basis.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a first-come, first-serve basis\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the most popular events have sold out and some of those remaining only have the more expensive tickets left.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most popular events\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"the more expensive tickets\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How much does it cost?\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tickets for some of the sessions and sports start at 24 euros, but medal sessions are more, upwards of 100 euros up to 990 euros for an athletics medal session including the women's heptathlon, men's and women's 4x100m relay final and the women's 400m final.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tickets\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"the sessions and sports start\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"24 euros\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"medal sessions\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"990 euros\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"an athletics medal session\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's heptathlon\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"4x100m relay\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 400m\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where are the venues?\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Paris the host city, and will have 12 of the venues, some of the sports will take place across the country.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4537688798134495e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The equestrian and modern pentathlon events will be held in the grounds of the Palace of Versailles.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.5678348442445155, \"rank\": 0.7610754431633361, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the grounds\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the Palace\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The national velodrome in Montigny-le-Bretonneux will hold track cycling and BMX, and the mountain bike track is also in the wider Paris region.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2348, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montigny-le-Bretonneux\", \"score\": 0.9999997211769303, \"rank\": 2.788230460214642e-07, \"text\": \"Montigny-le-Bretonneux\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montigny-le-Bretonneux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montigny-le-Bretonneux\"}, {\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"score\": 0.6555108618883231, \"rank\": 0.4524385855514665, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 2453, \"end\": 2458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4537688798134495e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The national velodrome\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"track cycling\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"the mountain bike track\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The football tournament will be held at six stadiums in other regions of France, Bordeaux, Nantes, Lyon, Saint-Etienne, Nice and Marseille.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.998645870358227, \"rank\": 0.001354244598619952, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2549, \"end\": 2557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\", \"score\": 0.9330770181892358, \"rank\": 0.07172289151611473, \"text\": \"Bordeaux\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\"}, {\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nantes\", \"score\": 0.8133683758026533, \"rank\": 0.22945522545089164, \"text\": \"Nantes\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nantes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nantes\"}, {\"begin\": 2567, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9818852719150527, \"rank\": 0.01844892535105425, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz_Cathedral\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.873311083350083e-15, \"text\": \"Saint-Etienne\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q1370598\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz_Cathedral\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz_Cathedral\"}, {\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OGC_Nice\", \"score\": 0.9885814137913891, \"rank\":